name: タヨ・ポーラ 🌸 (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)
text: [@joyarmadamba](https://twitter.com/joyarmadamba/) [@roytang](https://twitter.com/roytang/) Then at the level of account creation, there has to be more stringent verification steps para walang fake accounts. When I created my Grab account in 2012, I wasn't required to upload an ID. Perhaps to use any food delivery services, dapat verified human confirmed by a valid ID.
